{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":83,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"他们[信士们]靠在宝椅上观望[并说]："},{"SurahNumber":83,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"“不信仰的人们遭受他们所犯罪恶的还报了吗？”"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当天体破裂，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"听从其主命，必须听从时；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"当大地展开，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"抛出其中的一切，变成空虚，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"听从其主命，必须听从时；"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"人啊！你当为你的主[的道]而努力工作，你将会见到自己行为的结果。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"凡功过簿递给右手者，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他将受到简易的清算，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"他将兴高采烈地回去见家人。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"凡功过簿从背后递给者，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"他将叫苦连天，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他将被扔入烈火[中烧灼]。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"[在尘世时]，他在他的家人中原是快乐的，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他的确猜想他绝不会归到他的主那里去。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"不，他的主对他确是全视的。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"我以日落时的晚霞发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"以夜及其所掩藏的发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"以圆满时的月亮发誓，"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"你们必定从一个阶段[今世]到另一个阶段[后世]。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"他们为何不信仰呢？"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"当有人向他们诵读《古兰经》时，他们不叩头[注]。叩头处"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"其实，不信仰者是否认[注][安拉，穆圣，《古兰经》和伊斯兰教等]的。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"安拉最知道他们的心中所隐藏的[善恶]。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"因此，你当向他们宣布[他们必受]痛苦的刑罚。"},{"SurahNumber":84,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"唯信仰并行善者例外，他们将获得永恒的报酬[乐园]。"}]}